findings.message:
[Warning] The option Integer rounding mode in block Divide1 is set to Round instead of Simplest. Rounding methods other than Simplest may lead to abnormal/strange and difficult to debug rounding behavior (see example in documentation and ticket BTCM-668).
[Whitelisted] This rounding option has been chosen on purpose and shall remain active. Discussed and approved with A. Kallmeier and C. Kuscha

[Warning] The option Integer rounding mode in block Add4 is set to Ceiling instead of Simplest. Rounding methods other than Simplest may lead to abnormal/strange and difficult to debug rounding behavior (see example in documentation and ticket BTCM-668).
[Whitelisted] This rounding option has been chosen on purpose and shall remain active. Discussed and approved with A. Kallmeier and C. Kuscha
